<plot>A breathtaking story about two women who live in two different worlds but seek to conquer the same dream. Find out how music, fame and dreams interconnect the love and lives of the four main characters. When Eric discovers the potential of Sarah as a solo performer, will he also discover a new love in her? Seeing Sarah as a threat to her love and career, what schemes will Joanna use to destroy her competition? Meanwhile, when Marco realizes that the woman he loves is in love with someone else, will he give in and accept defeat? Or will he connive to get what he wants? And what fate does the mysterious -- and unfinished -- music sheet keep secret for the four main characters?</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?286619</url></doc>
